# アクセス制御1

### 動画内のプログラム
```java
// hello.java

public class Hero {
	String name;
	int hp;
	int money;

	public Hero(){
		this.name = "Hero";
		this.hp = 10;
	}

	public Hero(String name, int hp){
		this.name = name;
		this.hp = hp;
	}
}
```

```java
// main.java

public class Main {
	public  static void main(String[] args){
		Hero hero1 = new Hero("剣士", 100);
		Hero hero2 = new Hero("魔法使い", 50);

		hero1.money = 1000;
		hero2.money = 1000;

		System.out.println(hero1.name + "の所持金は" + hero1.money + "円");
		System.out.println(hero2.name + "の所持金は" + hero2.money + "円");

		System.out.println(hero1.name + "は敵を倒した");
		System.out.println(hero1.name + "は20円手に入れた");
		hero1.money += 20;

		System.out.println(hero1.name + "の所持金は" + hero1.money + "円");
		System.out.println(hero2.name + "の所持金は" + hero2.money + "円");
	}
}
```

